<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:13:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国对伊朗导弹和无人机计划支持者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-issues-sanctions-targeting-irans-missile-drone-program-facilitators-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国周二对五名个人和七个实体实施制裁，财政部称这些人是伊朗导弹和无人机计划的协助者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-issues-sanctions-targeting-irans-missile-drone-program-facilitators-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球——中国队东京失利后王健林和孙杨夺得混双金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-wang-sun-win-mixed-doubles-gold-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，在巴黎奥运会乒乓球混双决赛中，中国组合王楚钦/孙颖莎以4比2击败朝鲜组合李钟植/金锦勇，这是中国队横扫乒乓球金牌的第一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-wang-sun-win-mixed-doubles-gold-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>审计员称，奢华的国宴使法国总统陷入赤字</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/lavish-state-banquets-tip-french-presidency-into-red-auditor-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>公共审计办公室表示，法国总统马克龙的办公室去年因取消为英国国王查尔斯举办的豪华龙虾晚宴和其他国宴而超支了数百万欧元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:58:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/lavish-state-banquets-tip-french-presidency-into-red-auditor-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>Grifols 对中国股权减记了 4.94 亿美元的过去财务记录</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-revises-past-financial-records-with-equity-value-drop-494-mln-2024-07-30/</link><description>西班牙制药公司 Grifols 周二表示，其 2020-2023 年财务记录已减记 4.57 亿欧元（4.94 亿美元），以反映其所持中国公司上海莱士股份的价值。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-revises-past-financial-records-with-equity-value-drop-494-mln-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国表示对中国征收新关税将至少推迟两周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-start-new-china-tariffs-will-be-delayed-by-least-two-weeks-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国贸易代表办公室周二表示，美国对电动汽车及其电池、计算机芯片和医疗产品等一系列中国进口产品大幅提高关税的部分举措将至少推迟两周。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:39:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-start-new-china-tariffs-will-be-delayed-by-least-two-weeks-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>更多历史性的中国药检呈阳性给巴黎游泳运动蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/more-historic-china-positive-drug-tests-cast-cloud-over-paris-swimming-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，《纽约时报》报道称，两名游泳运动员在 2022 年的违禁类固醇检测中呈阳性，但由于检测结果被归咎于受污染的食品，他们的临时禁令被解除，中国因此再次陷入兴奋剂关注的焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/more-historic-china-positive-drug-tests-cast-cloud-over-paris-swimming-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>习近平祝贺委内瑞拉总统马杜罗连任</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-congratulates-venezuelas-maduro-reelection-2024-07-30/</link><description>官方媒体周二称，中国国家主席习近平祝贺委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗再次当选总统，这与一些拉美领导人和美国表达的怀疑和批评形成鲜明对比。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:45:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-congratulates-venezuelas-maduro-reelection-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>基辅邀请中国外长访问乌克兰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kyiv-invites-chinese-foreign-minister-visit-ukraine-2024-07-30/</link><description>基辅外交部发言人周二表示，乌克兰政府已邀请中国外交部长王毅访问乌克兰，北京方面表示对此提议“感兴趣”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kyiv-invites-chinese-foreign-minister-visit-ukraine-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国证监会执法局长晋升为副主席</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-regulator-likely-promote-law-enforcement-chief-vice-chair-sources-2024-07-30/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周二将其执法负责人提升为副主席，突显北京方面加强对其5.1万亿美元股市监管的决心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:15:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-regulator-likely-promote-law-enforcement-chief-vice-chair-sources-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>香港、澳门外国旅游团可免签进入海南</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-tour-groups-hong-kong-macau-can-enter-hainan-without-visa-2024-07-30/</link><description>据官方媒体周二报道，中国国家移民管理局表示，来自香港和澳门的两人或两人以上的外国旅游团可以免签在中国海南省停留最多六天。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-tour-groups-hong-kong-macau-can-enter-hainan-without-visa-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟秘书长博雷尔向越南提供南海安全支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/eu-wants-upgrade-ties-with-vietnam-foreign-policy-chief-borrell-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>欧盟外交政策负责人何塞普·博雷尔周二表示，欧盟希望保障南海和平，并告诉越南，欧盟可以帮助提高其海上安全和网络安全能力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:16:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/eu-wants-upgrade-ties-with-vietnam-foreign-policy-chief-borrell-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>梅洛尼为在华意大利企业寻求更好的条件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/meloni-seeks-better-terms-italian-firms-operating-china-2024-07-30/</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周二在退出“一带一路”计划后访华期间表示，她来华是为了加强与世界第二大经济体的合作并重置贸易关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/meloni-seeks-better-terms-italian-firms-operating-china-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统对中国发出警告，强调国防自力更生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-lai-says-chinas-threat-any-individual-country-is-threat-world-2024-07-30/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周二表示，中国对任何国家的威胁就是对世界的威胁，并补充说台湾将继续努力促进防御性自力更生和外国武器购买。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:53:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-lai-says-chinas-threat-any-individual-country-is-threat-world-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称与中国就渔民死亡问题达成协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-reaches-agreement-with-china-over-fishermens-deaths-2024-07-30/</link><description>经过几个月的谈判，台湾与中国周二就两名中国渔民在海事事件中丧生一事达成协议，此举可能会缓和敏感的台湾海峡的紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:51:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-reaches-agreement-with-china-over-fishermens-deaths-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>贸易部长称印度不会重新考虑允许中国投资的问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-rethinking-issue-allowing-chinese-investment-trade-minister-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>印度贸易部长皮尤什·戈亚尔周二表示，印度不会重新考虑允许中国投资的问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-rethinking-issue-allowing-chinese-investment-trade-minister-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>